</paragraph>
<paragraph id="AC3CCF97FB967AEFCD8AC0BB5C8A2F8F" pageNumber="769">measurements (mm) Major (Boraceia Biological Station, Sao Paulo state): HW 1.66, HL 1.76, SL 0.82, EL 0.20, PW 0.84. Holotype minor: HW 0.80, HL 0.84, SL 0.84, EL 0.12, PW 0.52.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="FE47D9485678348D34EB848C6BF910CD" pageNumber="769">Color Major: body and appendages clear light reddish yellow (&quot;orange&quot;), with gaster a shade darker. Minor: concolorous medium yellow brown, in both the Boraceia Biological Station series and holotype minor.</paragraph>
